seo.title: Women's Activewear | Women's Gym Clothes from Sears
seo.description: Buy women's sportwear at best prices from Sears. A complete collection of sweatshirts, team apparel, hoodies and more, will enhance your shopping experience.
seo.btf:
Enjoy a Better Workout with new Women's Activewear from Sears

Women's activewear can make exercising more comfortable and fun. You'll look and feel great in stylish women's gym clothes like jogging pants that let you run, stretch and squat with ease. Whether you're just getting started on your fitness journey and need the basics, like a Hanes cozy tee and some yoga pants, or want to customize your style with insulating layers and active sets, Sears has all the women's fitness wear you need for nearly any activity.

Specialized sports bras provide extra support for running or cross training. Layer one with a tank top or performance tank and high rise leggings for a quick gym outfit. Women's athletic wear is made from breathable fabrics that are designed to be as functional as they are stylish. If you're looking for a hint of understated fashion, you can opt for form-fitting joggers or a pair of shorts or yoga pants in a funky, geometrical print. A bright tee and flashy new women's athletic shoes will complete the look perfectly.

Insulating women's gym apparel like hoodies and sweatshirts are ideal for colder months when the temperature drops outside. The thick materials will keep your body warm when you're training. The right women's Champion gym apparel and fitness accessories from Sears and a little determination are all you need to work towards your fitness goals in style.
